init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The winner gets to live as a human, while the rest will be reincarnated as animals.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I’m not sure how I did it, but I’m one of the last people left.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The final round is a game of Russian roulette.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I’m going to live as a human!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They make me do things I would never do.
